## STRUCTURE DES DOSSIERS
```
Assets/_Project/
├── Scripts/
│   ├── Core/           → GameManager, SaveSystem
│   ├── Gameplay/       → DragDrop, Combat, Physics
│   ├── Characters/     → Stats, Passives
│   ├── Enemies/        → IA, Spawner
│   ├── Roguelike/      → Bonus, Salles, Shop
│   ├── UI/             → Menus, HUD
│   ├── Audio/          → AudioManager
│   └── Utils/          → Helpers, Pool, Extensions
├── ScriptableObjects/
│   ├── Characters/
│   ├── Enemies/
│   ├── Bonuses/
│   └── Config/
├── Prefabs/
├── Scenes/
├── Sprites/
├── Audio/
└── Resources/
```

